## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="3505d-141">次の例は、フレーズを認識する文法を作成後に「は、ワールド カップを勝ち抜いて民族」ワールド カップが勝利した国の名前。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3505d-141">The following example creates a grammar that recognizes the phrase "A nation that has won the World Cup is" followed by the name of a country that has won the World Cup.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3505d-142">例では、という名前の公開規則を作成します`WorldCupWinner`します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3505d-142">The example creates a public rule named `WorldCupWinner`.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3505d-143">例では、2 つ作成し、<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule>オブジェクト、`ruleEurope`と`ruleSAmerica`で渡し、<xref:System.String>ルール識別子の<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsElement>配列を含む、<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsOneOf>オブジェクト。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3505d-143">The example then creates two <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule> objects, `ruleEurope` and  `ruleSAmerica`, passing in a <xref:System.String> for the rule identifier and an <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsElement> array containing a <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsOneOf> object.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3505d-144">例を規則の参照を追加するその後、`ruleEurope`と`ruleSAmerica`ルールから`WorldCupWinner`します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3505d-144">Subsequently, the example adds rule references to `ruleEurope` and `ruleSAmerica` from the rule `WorldCupWinner`.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
public void WorldSoccerWinners ()  
{  
  // Create a grammar from an SRGSDocument, create a new rule  
  // and set its scope to public.  
  SrgsDocument srgsGrammar = new SrgsDocument ();  
  SrgsRule winnerRule = new SrgsRule ("WorldCupWinner");  
  winnerRule.Scope = SrgsRuleScope.Public;  
  
  // Add the introduction.  
  winnerRule.Elements.Add (new SrgsItem ("A nation that has won the world cup is"));  
  
  // Create the rule for the European nations.  
  SrgsOneOf oneOfEurope = new SrgsOneOf(new SrgsItem[] {new SrgsItem("England"), new SrgsItem("France"), new SrgsItem("Germany"), new SrgsItem("Italy")});  
  SrgsRule ruleEurope = (new SrgsRule("EuropeanNations", new SrgsElement[] {oneOfEurope}));  
  
  // Create the rule for the South American nations.  
  SrgsOneOf oneOfSAmerica = new SrgsOneOf(new SrgsItem[] {new SrgsItem("Argentina"), new SrgsItem("Brazil"), new SrgsItem("Uruguay")});  
  SrgsRule ruleSAmerica = (new SrgsRule("SouthAmericanNations", new SrgsElement[] {oneOfSAmerica}));  
  
  // Add references to winnerRule for ruleEurope and ruleSAmerica.  
  winnerRule.Elements.Add(new SrgsOneOf(new SrgsItem[] {(new SrgsItem (new SrgsRuleRef(ruleEurope))), new SrgsItem(new SrgsRuleRef(ruleSAmerica))}));  
  
  // Add all the rules to the grammar and make winnerRule  
  // the root rule of the grammar.  
  document.Rules.Add(new SrgsRule[] {winnerRule, ruleEurope, ruleSAmerica});  
  srgsGrammar.Root = winnerRule;  
}  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="3505d-145">作成した文法には、次の形式があります。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3505d-145">The created grammar has the following form.</span></span>  
  
```xml  
<grammar version="1.0" xml:lang="en-US" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2001/06/grammar" root="WorldCupWinner">  
    <rule id="WorldCupWinner" scope="public">  
        <item> A nation that has won the world cup is </item>  
        <one-of>  
            <item>  
                <ruleref uri="#EuropeanNations" />  
            </item>  
            <item>  
                <ruleref uri="#SouthAmericanNations" />  
            </item>  
        </one-of>  
    </rule>  
    <rule id="EuropeanNations">  
        <one-of>  
            <item> England </item>  
            <item> France </item>  
            <item> Germany </item>  
            <item> Italy </item>  
        </one-of>  
    </rule>  
    <rule id="SouthAmericanNations">  
        <one-of>  
            <item> Argentina </item>  
            <item> Brazil </item>  
            <item> Uruguay </item>  
        </one-of>  
    </rule>  
</grammar>  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="3505d-153">一般的な追加機能、<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule>オブジェクトが含まれます<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsItem>、 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsOneOf>、 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRuleRef>、および<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsToken>とスピーカーを指定するオブジェクト。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3505d-153">Typical additions to an <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule> object include <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsItem>, <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsOneOf>, <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRuleRef>, and <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsToken> objects that specify what speakers can say.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3505d-154">有効なルール要素には、認識可能なテキストの少なくとも 1 つまたは 1 つの規則の参照を含める必要があります。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3505d-154">A valid rule element must contain at least one piece of recognizable text or one rule reference.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3505d-155">参照してください[文法を使用して SrgsGrammar の作成](https://docs.microsoft.com/previous-versions/office/developer/speech-technologies/hh361680(v%3doffice.14))詳細についてはします。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3505d-155">See [Create Grammars Using SrgsGrammar](https://docs.microsoft.com/previous-versions/office/developer/speech-technologies/hh361680(v%3doffice.14)) for more information.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="3505d-156"><xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule>オブジェクトが含まれる場合も<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsNameValueTag>と<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsSemanticInterpretationTag>セマンティクス値とセマンティック キー、ルールを追加するオブジェクト。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3505d-156">An <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule> object may also contain <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsNameValueTag> and <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsSemanticInterpretationTag> objects that add semantic values and semantic keys to the rule.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3505d-157">音声認識エンジンには、フレーズを認識すると認識された語句と同様に、セマンティック情報を返すは。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3505d-157">The speech recognition engine will return the semantic information, as well as the recognized phrase, when it recognizes the phrase.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3505d-158">参照してください[解釈のセマンティック マークアップ](https://docs.microsoft.com/previous-versions/office/developer/speech-technologies/hh361595(v%3doffice.14))詳細についてはします。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3505d-158">See [Semantic Interpretation Markup](https://docs.microsoft.com/previous-versions/office/developer/speech-technologies/hh361595(v%3doffice.14)) for more information.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="3505d-159">次の例は、フレーズを認識する文法を作成後に「は、ワールド カップを勝ち抜いて民族」ワールド カップが勝利した国の名前。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3505d-159">The following example creates a grammar that recognizes the phrase "A nation that has won the World Cup is" followed by the name of a country that has won the World Cup.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3505d-160">作成した後、<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule>オブジェクト`winnerRule`文字列識別子を付けます`WorldCupWinner`、例では、<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule.Add%2A>文字列を追加する方法のルールに「ワールド カップを勝ち抜いて民族は」。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3505d-160">After creating the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule> object `winnerRule` and giving it the string identifier `WorldCupWinner`, the example uses the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule.Add%2A> method to append the string  "A nation that has won the World Cup is" to the rule.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3505d-161">追加の 2 つの規則を作成し`ruleEurope`と`ruleSAmerica`します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3505d-161">The example then creates two additional rules, `ruleEurope` and  `ruleSAmerica`.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3505d-162">使用してもう一度、<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule.Add%2A>メソッドの例では、追加、<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsOneOf>オブジェクトを`WorldCupWinner`ルール参照を含むルール`ruleEurope`と`ruleSAmerica`します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3505d-162">Again using the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule.Add%2A> method, the example appends an <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsOneOf> object to the `WorldCupWinner` rule that contains rule references to `ruleEurope` and `ruleSAmerica`.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
// Create an SrgsDocument, create a new rule  
// and set its scope to public.  
SrgsDocument document = new SrgsDocument();  
SrgsRule winnerRule = new SrgsRule("WorldCupWinner");  
winnerRule.Scope = SrgsRuleScope.Public;  
  
// Add the introduction.  
winnerRule.Elements.Add(new SrgsItem("A nation that has won the world cup is: "));  
  
// Create the rule for the European nations.  
SrgsOneOf oneOfEurope = new SrgsOneOf(new SrgsItem[] {new SrgsItem("England"), new SrgsItem("France"), new SrgsItem("Germany"), new SrgsItem("Italy")});  
SrgsRule ruleEurope = (new SrgsRule("EuropeanNations", new SrgsElement[] {oneOfEurope}));  
  
// Create the rule for the South American nations.  
SrgsOneOf oneOfSAmerica = new SrgsOneOf(new SrgsItem[] {new SrgsItem("Argentina"), new SrgsItem("Brazil"), new SrgsItem("Uruguay")});  
SrgsRule ruleSAmerica = (new SrgsRule("SouthAmericanNations", new SrgsElement[] {oneOfSAmerica}));  
  
// Add references to winnerRule for ruleEurope and ruleSAmerica.  
winnerRule.Elements.Add(new SrgsOneOf(new SrgsItem[] {(new SrgsItem (new SrgsRuleRef(ruleEurope))), new SrgsItem(new SrgsRuleRef(ruleSAmerica))}));  
  
// Add all the rules to the document and make winnerRule   
// the root rule of the document.  
document.Rules.Add(new SrgsRule[] {winnerRule, ruleEurope, ruleSAmerica});  
document.Root = winnerRule;  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="3505d-192">スコープの既定値は`Private`します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3505d-192">The default value for scope is `Private`.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3505d-193">プライベートのルールは、その含まれる文法のルート ルールから、またはルート ルールから参照されている別の規則から規則の参照によって認識のみアクティブにできます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3505d-193">A private rule can only be activated for recognition by a rule reference from the root rule in its containing grammar or from another rule that is referenced from the root rule.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3505d-194">プライベート ルールは、その含まれる文法のルート規則として、プライベートの規則が宣言されていない限り、外部文法で参照できません。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3505d-194">A private rule cannot be referenced by an external grammar, unless the private rule is declared as the root rule of its containing grammar.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="3505d-195">そのスコープに設定されている場合`Public`、<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule>から参照によって認識のオブジェクトをアクティブにできる、<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRuleRef>包含する文法または外部の文法でルールからのオブジェクト。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3505d-195">If its scope is set to `Public`, an <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule> object can be activated for recognition by a reference from a <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRuleRef> object in the containing grammar or from a rule in an external grammar.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="3505d-196">次の例は、フレーズを認識する文法を作成後に「は、ワールド カップを勝ち抜いて民族」ワールド カップが勝利した国の名前。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3505d-196">The following example creates a grammar that recognizes the phrase "A nation that has won the World Cup is" followed by the name of a country that has won the World Cup.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3505d-197">という名前の公開規則を作成、`WorldCupWinner`し、そのルールのスコープをパブリックに設定します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3505d-197">It creates a public rule named `WorldCupWinner` and sets the scope of that rule to Public.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
// Create an SrgsDocument, create a new rule and set its scope to public.  
SrgsDocument document = new SrgsDocument();  
SrgsRule winnerRule = new SrgsRule("WorldCupWinner");  
winnerRule.Scope = SrgsRuleScope.Public;  
  
// Add the introduction.  
winnerRule.Elements.Add(new SrgsItem("A nation that has won the world cup is: "));  
  
// Create the rule for the European nations.  
SrgsOneOf oneOfEurope = new SrgsOneOf(new SrgsItem[] {new SrgsItem("England"), new SrgsItem("France"), new SrgsItem("Germany"), new SrgsItem("Italy")});  
SrgsRule ruleEurope = (new SrgsRule("EuropeanNations", new SrgsElement[] {oneOfEurope}));  
  
// Create the rule for the South American nations.  
SrgsOneOf oneOfSAmerica = new SrgsOneOf(new SrgsItem[] {new SrgsItem("Argentina"), new SrgsItem("Brazil"), new SrgsItem("Uruguay")});  
SrgsRule ruleSAmerica = (new SrgsRule("SouthAmericanNations", new SrgsElement[] {oneOfSAmerica}));  
  
// Add references to winnerRule for ruleEurope and ruleSAmerica.  
winnerRule.Elements.Add(new SrgsOneOf(new SrgsItem[] {(new SrgsItem (new SrgsRuleRef(ruleEurope)), new SrgsItem(new SrgsRuleRef(ruleSAmerica)})));  
  
// Add all the rules to the document and make winnerRule   
// the root rule of the document.  
document.Rules.Add(new SrgsRule[] {winnerRule, ruleEurope, ruleSAmerica});  
document.Root = winnerRule;  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="3505d-198">作成した文法には、次の形式があります。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3505d-198">The created grammar has the following form.</span></span>  
  
